-- Turkey to Auction 34 Geothermal, Mineral Water Sites, Dunya Says
-- B y   E m r e   P e k e r
-- 2011-12-16T07:21:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-16/turkey-to-auction-34-geothermal-mineral-water-sites-dunya-says.html
Turkey  will auction 34 geothermal
and mineral water springs within a month to improve usage of
natural resources, Dunya reported.  The government will take bids for 19 sites in Ankara on
Dec. 28 and for 15 locations in the western province of Aydin on
Jan. 3, the Istanbul-based newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Emre Peker in Ankara at 
 epeker2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
